    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Fuinjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 3</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 16 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 4 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 16</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H, E</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>A seal holds the closeable object shut (such as a book, a pouch, a door, etc.), preventing it from being opened by anyone.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 3 Chakra to add a password or code to the seal. If the seal is broken without applying the code or password, the sealed object is destroyed.</p>\n\n",
